    "description": "<i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/32088dccdc1d921b7b713e0bc06b6e8b.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=338 /></span> 欢迎参与激烈战斗的团队射击游戏！</h2></i>欢迎来到即将展开的《第二浪潮》世界，参与团队射击游戏的激烈战斗！我们将结合团队射击游戏的最佳元素，为您带来与任何游戏都无法比拟的刺激游戏体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/9bf0fd869dda92d2373cb35a53cd525b.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/03a254635edad0bf7ed96fac07248c28.poster.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/03a254635edad0bf7ed96fac07248c28.webm?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/03a254635edad0bf7ed96fac07248c28.mp4?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 令人兴奋的亚尔曼蒂亚故事</h2></i>通过40万字的小说，探索亚尔曼蒂亚的历史和围绕《第二浪潮》的传说。与小说中的角色相遇，参与战场获取神奇矿石。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/2b56c5193eb0d370f5e95e16b744d18f.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/9f5232223b55715ee7f241d18e1839b8.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=230 /></span> 丰富的英雄角色，独特的战斗方式</h2></i>每个角色都有着不同的战斗方式，从强大的肉盾、勇猛的战士到灵活的狙击手、神秘的魔法师、隐秘的刺客以及可靠的辅助者，每位玩家都能找到适合自己风格的英雄角色。每位英雄都能立刻进入战斗，且一些英雄还具备在游戏中切换角色的能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/4d67b4b1a7bf4b5bfdadafa74de3c733.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>目前有三种模式可供选择，可以根据小队配置和游戏风格整合各种策略。<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/f960154d3fcdeaee30992bf992dba5d3.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span> 沉浸式 6vs6 多人战斗</h2></i>两支队伍在特里斯汀城市中心，围绕着高耸的能源核心展开战斗，以夺取核心为目标。持续战斗，夺取核心以获得神奇矿石的力量。为了获胜，您必须占领据点或击败徘徊的怪物以率先获得1000分。<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/04a5517b3202d4cb617e664f668cf840.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span> 最佳的  4vs4vs4 多人游戏体验</h2></i>在红色马戏团内隐藏的神奇矿石上，四支队伍展开竞争激烈的独特挑战。要获胜，您必须击败另两支队伍或占领两个据点以获得1500分。<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/76e207e99721fea742af545643237b88.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span> 独一无二的 3vs3vs3vs3 战斗</h2></i>参与夺取神奇矿石争夺战，与其他三支队伍竞争。只要您的队友收集了24块以上的神奇矿石并持有超过一定时间，就可以获胜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/a12f3ebf2338808b841952570ed83ada.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.poster.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.webm?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.mp4?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 根据角色概念量身定制的不同的服装</h2></i>在《第二浪潮》商店的商店中，您可以购买游戏每个角色发独特皮肤、演绎效果和角色语音。快穿上您喜欢的角色服装，在战斗中大显身手吧！Challengers Games 工作室将不断努力为您提供公平和平衡的游戏体验。",
